profile:
With several years of experience in Property & Casualty Insurance and in structural and Business Risk Management, our inspections have the advantage of knowledge and experience. We are an InterNACHI Certified Home Inspector with additional certification for conducting COVID Safe inspections. 

One can get a free quote online from our website and after you have made up your mind you can book it online.
The process which the inspector does while inspecting your house is very informative. 
There are no hidden charges, no obligation, and the work is done on a full-time basis.

MISSION STATEMENT
We offer more than an affordable and certified home inspection: we strive to give our clients the safety, peace of mind, and advantage that will result in their best buying, selling, and/or homeownership experience.

189 Inglewood Cres. Thunder Bay ON P7C 2E8 Canada
Email us : arladouc@gmail.com
Call us : 8076289326
services: HOME INSPECTION, FURNACE INSPECTION, INFRARED (IR) INSPECTION, DECK INSPECTION, ROOF INSPECTION, FOUNDATION INSPECTION, ELECTRICAL INSPECTION, PLUMBING INSPECTION, PEST CONTROL INSPECTION
memberships: InterNACHI, Thunder Bay Real Estate Board
